name: Tempest Scout 2
Lore: 'Assigned to coordinate battle activities with the Endor biker scout detachment. Enclosed. First saw battle in Kashyyyk forests.',
Text: 'Deploy -1 to Endor. May add 2 pilots or passengers. May move as a ''react''. Immune to attrition < 3 when Marquand piloting. Your scouts may move here as a ''react''.',
